These files are unmodified upstream Lua test scripts, used here only as the
conformance oracle for migrating this fork from Lua 5.1 to 5.4 semantics.
Re-fetch / bump with:  make lua54-tests  (LUA54_TESTS_VER=5.4.x to override)
Run against the engine:  make lua54-conformance   (or: go run ./cmd/lua54conformance)
